               <msContents class="lemmatic">
                  <summary>This manuscript contains commentary on the book of Aphorisms attributed to <persName type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/287984736" key="person_287984736">Hippocrates</persName>.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="MS_280-item1">
                     <author key="person_90068840">
                        <persName ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/90068840" type="aut">Ibn al-Quffابن القف الكركي</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="en" key="work_7761">Ibn al-Quff's commentary on the Hippocratic Aphorisms</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7761">Šarḥ Fuṣūl Abuqrāṭ li Ibn al-Quff</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_7761">شرح فصول أبقراط لابن القف الكركي</title>
                     <note>Original manuscript in Bibl. Or. de l'Université Saint-Joseph.</note>
                     <note>This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on f. 6b; the beginning of each Book is as follows: Bk1: 6b; Bk2: 59a; Bk3: 134a; Bk4: 182b; Bk5: 256b; Bk6: 314b; Bk7: 347b.</note>
